    {"id": "api-pub-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 942, "width": 390, "height": 76, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1040, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1040, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "api-pub", "originalText": "Público (Next proxy): GET /api/catalog, GET /api/stores, POST /api/shipping,\nPOST /api/checkout/preview, POST /api/checkout.\nBrowser pode usar NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL para vitrine/checkout.", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "s4-label", "type": "text", "x": 100, "y": 1055, "width": 400, "height": 25, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1041, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1041, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": null, "originalText": "4. Comunicação Back–Front", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "comm-1", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 1092, "width": 500, "height": 100, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1042, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1042, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false},
    {"id": "comm-1-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 1098, "width": 470, "height": 88, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1043, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1043, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "comm-1", "originalText": "• Front chama apenas o próprio host (Next.js).\n• Next route handlers fazem fetch ao backend (API_URL em server).\n• Admin/portal: adminFetch → /api/admin/* (cookie automático).\n• Respostas JSON; erros com status HTTP e mensagem.", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "s5-label", "type": "text", "x": 100, "y": 1225, "width": 260, "height": 25, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1044, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1044, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": null, "originalText": "5. Fluxos por área", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "flow-vitrine", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 1262, "width": 340, "height": 58, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1045, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1045, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false},
    {"id": "flow-vitrine-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 1268, "width": 310, "height": 46, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1046, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1046, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "flow-vitrine", "originalText": "Vitrine: /vitrine/[slug], /vitrine/[slug]/[store].\nGET /api/catalog, GET /api/stores.", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "flow-checkout", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 1332, "width": 340, "height": 82, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1047, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1047, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false},
    {"id": "flow-checkout-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 1338, "width": 310, "height": 70, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1048, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1048, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "flow-checkout", "originalText": "Checkout: catalog + stores → preview → shipping/quote → POST /checkout.\nBackend: valida tenant/loja/estoque/frete; grava pedido; notificações.", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "flow-portal", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 1426, "width": 340, "height": 82, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1049, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1049, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false},
    {"id": "flow-portal-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 1432, "width": 310, "height": 70, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1050, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1050, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "flow-portal", "originalText": "Portal: login → auth/me + guards. Módulos: pedidos, catálogo, lojas,\nestoque, campanhas, insights, mensagens, billing via /api/admin/*.", "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"id": "flow-admin", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 1520, "width": 340, "height": 58, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1051, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1051, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false},
    {"id": "flow-admin-t", "type": "text", "x": 115, "y": 1526, "width": 310, "height": 46, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1052, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1052, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 18, "containerId": "flow-admin", "originalText": "Admin central: /admin. Super admin → /api/admin/central/* (tenants, planos).", "lineHeight": 1.25},
